      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/89/5444",
      "text": [
        " : سَأَلْتُ أَبَا جَعْفَرٍ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ عَنِ اَلرَّجُلِ يُفَضِّلُ بَعْضَ وُلْدِهِ عَلَى بَعْضٍ قَالَ \"نَعَمْ وَ نِسَاءَهُ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5444 - It is narrated from Abdullah ibn Muhammad Al-Hajjal from Thaʿlabah ibn Maymun from Muhammad ibn Qays, who said: I asked Abu Jafar Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) about a man who gives preference to some of his children over others.\nImam (as) replied: \"Yes, and he may also favor some of his wives (over other wives).\""
        ]
      }
    },
